      This software uses
      - rsync (Andrew Tridgell and Paul Mackerrasas), <http://lists.samba.org>
      - fpart (Ganael LAPLANCHE <ganael.laplanche@martymac.org>), 
          <https://github.com/martymac/fpart>
      - perfquery < hal.rosenstock [at] gmail.com >
